data.description: Here's the perfect opportunity for those of you who are looking for a affordable home in Troy w/good bones and in a desirable neighborhood~ This charming brick ranch can be easily transformed with a few cosmetic updates~ Open floor plan is flowing & functional with 1738 Sq. Ft.~ Finished basement for additional living space has a large open area w/bar. 2 1/2 car detached garage for all your cars, tools & toys~Don't miss this amazing opportunity to make this this your home and easily turn this investment into instant equity! Updated homes in area are selling much higher. Come put your shine on this amazing opportunity!
